title: WTA Premier, Doha Women's Singles Results
text: February 15, 2018 / 8:00 PM / Updated 4 hours ago WTA Premier, Doha Women's Singles Results Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 15 (OPTA) - Results from the WTA Premier, Doha Women's Singles matches on Thursday .. 3rd Round .. 1-Caroline Wozniacki (DEN) beat Monica Niculescu (ROU) 7-5 6-1 8-Angelique Kerber (GER) beat 10-Johanna Konta (GBR) 1-6 6-1 6-3 16-Petra Kvitova (CZE) beat 3-Elina Svitolina (UKR) 6-4 7-5 9-Julia Goerges (GER) beat Mihaela Buzarnescu (ROU) 6-2 6-2 7-Caroline Garcia (FRA) beat Anna Blinkova (RUS) 7-6(3) 7-5 4-Garbine Muguruza (ESP) beat Sorana Cirstea (ROU) 6-0 6-4 Catherine Bellis (USA) beat 5-Karolina Pliskova (CZE) 7-6(4) 6-3 2-Simona Halep (ROU) beat 13-Anastasija Sevastova 6-4 6-3 (LAT)
